        <abstract>
            <p>Is "awfully glad" at LD’s appointment [as an instructor at Chatham].</p>
            <p>Thinks LD should start reading chemistry "though reading does not do much".</p>
            <p>Reports scientific work of George and Frank Darwin.</p>
